description: Use frozen stir-fry vegetables to make this speedy dinner option. It's packed with ginger, beef, almonds and fresh greens for a tasty bowl of yum.
name: Easy Almond & Beef Noodle StirFry Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 100 g Cantonese beef stirfry sauce sachet

recipeInstructions.text: Add beef and almonds and stirfry for 1 minute or until heated through. Serve topped with coriander and spring onion.
